ory review of the UK’s party and election finance laws. Recommendations for change. June 2013. </span><a href="http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/__data/assets/pdf_file/0008/157499/PEF-Regulatory-Review-2013.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/__data/assets/pdf_file/0008/157499/PEF-Regulatory-Review-2013.pdf</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span></p></body></html>